data.description: Welcome to this charming 2000+ sq ft home, nestled at the end of a peaceful dead-end street in Orange Park. Boasting 3 bedrooms and a versatile flex space. The design seamlessly connects the living area, kitchen, and separate dining room. The master suite offers a private retreat while while two additional bedrooms provide flexibility for guests or family. The property sits on JUST UNDER an acre with NO HOA. This home also offers a flex space - perfect for a home office or an extra bedroom. Outside, the expansive backyard invites outdoor relaxation, complemented by a two-car garage for convenience and security. Don't miss the chance to make this home your own - schedule your visit today and experience gracious living in this idyllic setting.
